about: Dinner, lunch, cocktails, expositions, clubnights and much more on the top floor of the old Volkskrantbuilding. Open daily!
name: Canvasopde7e
public_transit:
Tram:
Tram 3 stops at the corner of Wibautstraat/ Ruyschstraat. Walk in southern direction and find at your right hand the former Volkskrant building.

Subway:
# 51, 53 and 54 stop in front the door at the stop Wibautstraat. Take the exit Grensstraat. The last stop is at 0.39 AM.

Train:
Canvasopde7e is at 10 minutes from the Amstel Station. The last train stops here at 1:01 AM. Walk from the station to the Prins Berhardsquare (roundabout). Take the the third exit: the Wibautstraat. Canvasopde7e will be found after the viaduct at your left side.

Nightbus:
Bus 355 goes from Central Station to the Bijlmermeer and stops at the corner of Wibautstraat/Ruyschstraat. Walk from the stop Wibautstraat in southern direction. On your rightside after ±300mtrs you find Canvasopde7e.
